<br>
And now that all the gnomes are either looking at me crossly or getting ready to attack, I'd also like to say Welcome to being a wizard!!!!<br>
<br>
As for diety, I rather enjoy the influence of Quellious the Tranquil.<br>
<br>
As for responsibilities, nuke, do your best not to get aggro as it's rather annoying to have everyone tell you to stop nuking too early (even if you aren't nuking too early and the main tank is an idiot who doesn't know how to KEEP aggro, but, er aside from that), nuke some more and enjoy the freedom of gating around!!!<br>
<br>
Oh, and I must be the only caster around who doesn't think that low levels need KEI, Aego or even Virtue, etc.  I'll be happy if they implement that level requirement for these spells to stick on a character on the regular servers.  I'm tired of all these low leveled people shooting up and saying how easy it is to be a wizard without having actually learned how to fight and live.  High buffs do not belong on low characters.  That's my rant for today.<br>
<br>
